    <item>
      <title>德国铁路公司就价值 150 亿欧元的物流部门进行新投标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/deutsche-bahn-invites-fresh-bids-for-15-billion-logistics-arm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国铁路公司正在要求一组选定的竞标者为其德铁信可物流部门提交另一轮不具约束力的报价，该部门的估值可能高达 150 亿欧元（160 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/deutsche-bahn-invites-fresh-bids-for-15-billion-logistics-arm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国将援助欧洲太阳能电池板制造商以削弱中国的主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/france-to-aid-europe-s-solar-panel-makers-to-reduce-china-s-dominance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府将修改法规并提供补贴，支持安装国产太阳能电池板，这是其能源转型的关键，以削弱中国设备制造商的主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/france-to-aid-europe-s-solar-panel-makers-to-reduce-china-s-dominance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔莫蒂表示欧洲不能依靠危机来促进银行合并</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ermotti-says-europe-can-t-rely-on-crises-to-prompt-bank-mergers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团的塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂表示，除非欧盟完成统一银行和资本市场的工作，否则欧洲银行将无法与华尔街竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ermotti-says-europe-can-t-rely-on-crises-to-prompt-bank-mergers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最大的黄金矿商错过了金价创纪录的上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/biggest-gold-miners-are-missing-out-on-bullion-s-record-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的黄金矿商斥资数十亿美元成为以黄金为重点的投资者的明显家园，因此面临着错失黄金创纪录涨幅的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/biggest-gold-miners-are-missing-out-on-bullion-s-record-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务所有者债务违约，危机加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/thames-water-owner-kemble-sends-default-notice-to-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司的控股公司因未能支付利息而拖欠了约 14 亿英镑（17 亿美元）的债务，这是英国最大水务公司危机的最新升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/thames-water-owner-kemble-sends-default-notice-to-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:07:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着交易员推迟首次降息，国债抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/beaten-down-bond-traders-are-betting-jobs-data-means-more-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，债券交易员的开局不利，因为数据显示美国劳动力市场活跃，几乎没有可能促使美联储降息的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/beaten-down-bond-traders-are-betting-jobs-data-means-more-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 09:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据显示美国正在向前发展，股市上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份井喷的就业报告表明美国经济将继续为美国企业提供动力之后，股市本周以积极的势头结束。即使这意味着利率仍有可能上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
